          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/wuyeti/" class=" " title="许自然">许自然</a>
                (坚心一志任前程 大道于人终不负)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="40253778">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">注云：吕才叙禄命载《新唐书 吕才传》
案：叙在旧唐书</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-11-16 21:32</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                注云：吕才叙禄命载《新唐书 吕才传》<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>案：叙在旧唐书
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

